    "user_title": "Convert HTML to High-Fidelity PDFs with RTL Support",
    "value_statement": "Converting HTML to PDF often breaks layouts, loses fonts, or fails with right-to-left scripts. This skill uses headless Chrome to produce pixel-perfect PDFs from any HTML source, with automatic detection and support for Hebrew and Arabic.",
    "seo_keywords": [
      "HTML to PDF",
      "Puppeteer PDF",
      "RTL PDF support",
      "Hebrew PDF converter",
      "Arabic PDF converter",
      "Claude Code skill",
